Package com.j256.ormlite.stmt.query

Interface Summary
Clause Internal marker class for query clauses.
NeedsFutureClause Internal interface which defines a clause that consumes a future clause.
 

Class Summary
Between Internal class handling the SQL 'between' query part.
In Internal class handling the SQL 'in' query part.
IsNotNull Internal class handling the SQL 'IS NOT NULL' comparison query part.
IsNull Internal class handling the SQL 'IS NULL' comparison query part.
ManyClause For operations with a number of them in a row.
Not Internal class handling the SQL 'NOT' boolean comparison operation.
OrderBy  
Raw Raw part of the where to just stick in a string in the middle of the WHERE.
SetExpression  
SetValue  
SimpleComparison Internal class handling a simple comparison query part where the operation is passed in.
